Open cupboard in the kitchen 
Take out Electrical Pot with 1 L capacity from cupboard
Close cupboard
Open the fridge 
Bring one 500 ml bottle of water from the fridge
if , there is no water,
go and buy a 500 ml water bottle. 
open the water bottle 
Bring the water bottle above the pot 
Telte the water bottle towards the pot to let the water drop in the pot
Keep pouring water until the water water bottle is empty 
Take back the water bottle and place it on the table 
Take the pot and connect is with electricity 
Turn on the electrical switch on
if  the water makes bubbles and sounds. 
Unplug the pot from electricity,
Else, wait 2 more minutes.
Repeat 14. 
Unplug the porter pot from the electricity.
Take the Electrical Pot and insert it on the kitchen table. 
Open cupboard and bring a cup
Put the water into a cup 
Put back the Electrical Pot in the cupboard
